flowchart TD
  A[GitHub Actions schedule or manual run] --> B[Read Jira security queue]
  B --> C[For each To Do / In Progress GHAS ticket]
  C --> D[Parse tool, repo, alert number]
  D --> E[Fetch GHAS alert with GHAS_TRIAGE_GITHUB_TOKEN]
  E -->|Dependabot fixed/withdrawn/missing| FP[Fast path: 1-line comment + close no LLM]
  E -->|fetch fails| F[Post 1-line fetch/error note]
  E -->|fetch succeeds| G[Agentic evidence layers]
  G --> H[Repo profile]
  G --> I[Advisory/API extraction]
  G --> J[Code search + manifests + lockfiles]
  G --> K[README + Docker + CI + runtime hints]
  G --> L[Blame / last commit authors]
  G --> M[Org-wide package usage]
  G --> OH[Org-wide deploy/infra discovery]
  G --> GM[Global memory triage history]
  G --> S[External Skills Library]
  H --> N[Evidence matrix]
  I --> N
  J --> N
  K --> N
  L --> N
  M --> N
  OH --> N
  GM --> N
  S --> N
  N --> TT[Pre-flight truth table tier + force verdict]
  TT --> O[Final Judge LLM or force verdict no LLM]
  O --> PR[ProsecutorAgent adversarial review]
  PR --> X[Silent CriticAgent]
  X --> P[Consistency gate]
  P --> Q[Post, skip, learn, and transition]
  Q --> R[Append triage history + update Jira issue property]
